summary: Discovery Channel about the nature of Skyrim
descriptionHtml:
Hello nexus dovakins!
I want present to your attention two little videos. They are similar and different at the same time. You can identify the distinctive features if you watch this video. I hope you like it, of course).

The first of this is documental film about wild nature of the Tamriel\'s north province. The main role plays Ignat Trofimovich Mamontoff - snow elf 80 lvl. Guest star - self-confident blood dragon.  This sketch was made spontaneously by means of a first-person view, without the use of any console commands; and this is the main value and the main difference from my second work - Nordog saga ---> http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7158

Enjoy!
author: FilmCraft
